query:
UPDATE calendar_events SET
                start_ts = $2,
                duration = $3,
                end_ts = $4,
                busy = $5,
                created = $6,
                updated = $7,
                recurrence = $8,
                exdates = $9,
                reminders = $10,
                service_uid = $11,
                metadata = $12
            WHERE event_uid = $1
